Open VS Code.
Press Ctrl + , to open Settings.
Search for:
terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux
Click "Edit in settings.json" and set it to Bash:
"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux": "bash"
Restart VS Code.
âœ… Now all new VS Code terminals will open in Bash.
